body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! Thank you for reaching out to Data Cars. My name is Jesse Sanders. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Judith! Can you please provide me with your phone number? I need to update our records.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my phone number is six five five, eight seven two, three four one two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Judith. And may I also have your email address? It will help us keep you informed about our latest offers.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my email address is judith.morgan@example.com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for sharing that. We'll update our system with this information. If you have any questions, feel free to ask.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I appreciate your help, Jesse. I was quite surprised by the issue, but your assistance has been valuable.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm glad I could help, Judith. Thank you for your time. If you need further assistance, don't hesitate to contact us. Have a great day!

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you, Jesse. Have a wonderful day too!
